        At Event4U, we believe every event tells a story, and we strive to make each one extraordinary. Whether it's a grand-scale celebration or an intimate gathering, our commitment to excellence and innovation makes us the go-to choice for event planning.
    </p>
</section>

<!-- Why Event4U Section -->
<section class="scroll-reveal">
